79
0:03:47.753,000 --> 0:03:48,000
Amazon.

80
0:03:48.937,000 --> 0:03:5,000
You get more for less into your gut;

81
0:03:51.105,000 --> 0:03:54,000
digest, send it to your muscular and skeletal system of consumption.

82
0:03:54.911,000 --> 0:03:55,000
Moving further,

83
0:03:56.59,000 --> 0:03:59,000
once we know we will survive, the basic instinct,

84
0:04:00.219,000 --> 0:04:02,000
